# NO LIABILITY WILL BE  ACCEPTED BY SUN MICROSYSTEMS FOR ANY LOSS (DIRECT
# OR CONSEQUENTIAL) INCURRED IN ANY WAY BY ANY PARTY THROUGH THE USE OF
# THIS INFORMATION.
